---- MODULE WindowGuardPlusCal ----
\* Window guard mode — prevents accidental close or resize when a critical operation is in progress.
\* PlusCal version — generated by tlaiser
\* https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

CONSTANTS Free, Locked, ReadOnly

